  <WebPartDescription>
    <![CDATA[This web part processes forum unsubscription requests submitted by users and displays a confirmation message.]]>
  </WebPartDescription>
  <WebPartDisplayName>Forum unsubscription</WebPartDisplayName>
  <WebPartDocumentation>
<![CDATA[
<p>The web part can be used to create a forum unsubscription page with a custom&nbsp;design that&nbsp;will be used instead of the&nbsp;default system page.&nbsp;The URL of such a page can be assigned to individual forum groups or forums through their <strong><span class="FieldLabel" id="m_c_forumEdit_lblUnsubscriptionUrl">Forum unsubscription URL</span></strong> property, or globally in <strong>Settings -&gt; Community -&gt; Forums -&gt; Forum unsubscription URL</strong>. Once assigned, the unsubscription links in the notifications for the given forums leads to the page. There, the web part automatically processes the query string parameters and performs the&nbsp;required unsubscription.</p>

]]>
  </WebPartDocumentation>
  <WebPartFileName>Forums/ForumUnsubscription.ascx</WebPartFileName>
